Package: ffscrapr
Type: Package
Title: FFscrapR - R Client for Fantasy Football League APIs
Version: 0.0.4.6
Authors@R: person("Tan", "Ho", email = "tan@tanho.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The goal of this package is to abstract the code required to call various Fantasy Football APIs (i.e. MFL, Sleeper, Fleaflicker, ESPN, Yahoo) and create methods that handle any authentication required, form appropriate calls, and return tidy & predictable data which can be easily connected to DynastyProcess and FantasyPros information.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports:
  httr  (>= 1.4.0),
  purrr (>= 0.3.0),
  glue (>= 1.3.0),
  jsonlite (>= 1.5.0), 
  ratelimitr (>= 0.4.0)
